            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Antonius Cerdonis <expan><abbr>lib</abbr><ex>ertus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Fortunatus sibi et Noniae </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Crhesime <note>sic</note> coniugi optumae <lb n="2"/>bene merenti feminae et <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> Antonio Cerdoni patrono suo et <lb n="4"/>Euhodo <expan><abbr>lib</abbr><ex>erto</ex></expan> et Adiecto <expan><abbr>lib</abbr><ex>erto</ex></expan> et <lb n="5"/>Heraclae <expan><abbr>lib</abbr><ex>ertae</ex></expan> et Primae <expan><abbr>lib</abbr><ex>ertae</ex></expan> et <lb n="6"/>Noniae Chresimes <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibertae</ex></expan> Fortunatae <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibertae</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>et <expan><abbr>A</abbr><ex>ulo</ex></expan> Cossinio Eutycho amico <lb n="8"/>libertis <expan><abbr>libertabusq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> suis
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(C): Sieht in Nonia Fortunata eine Person, die von Nonia Chresime freigelassen wurde.</p>
            </div>
